Package me.normanmaurer.niosmtp.delivery.callback

Interface Summary
SMTPResponseCallbackFactory A Factory which is responsible for return the right SMTPResponseCallback depending on the state of the SMTPSession and the SMTPRequest or SMTPMessage
 

Class Summary
AbstractAuthResponseCallback Abstract base class of AbstractResponseCallback which AUTH callbacks should use
AbstractPipelineResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which should get sub-classed by implementations which may be used within the PIPELINING context.
AbstractResponseCallback Abstract base implementation of SMTPResponseCallback which comple the SMTPDeliveryFuture on an Exception
AuthLoginResponseCallback AbstractAuthResponseCallback which handles AUTH LOGIN
AuthPlainResponseCallback AbstractAuthResponseCallback which should be used to handle AUTH PLAIN
DataResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the DATA SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
EhloResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the EHLO SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
LMTPPostDataResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback which handles the SMTPResponse for the DATA finish sequence in the LMTP protocol
LMTPResponseCallbackFactory SMTPResponseCallbackFactory implementation which returns the SMTPResponseCallback's while processing the LMTP Transaction
LMTPWelcomeResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback which will be used after the welcome SMTPResponse was sent from the LMTP Server
MailResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the MAIL SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
PostDataResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the POST DATA SMTPResponse which will get send after the SMTPMessage get submitted via the CRLF.CRLF sequence
RcptResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the RCPT SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
SMTPResponseCallbackFactoryImpl  
StartTlsResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the STARTLS SMTPResponse It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
WelcomeResponseCallback AbstractResponseCallback implementation which will handle the WELCOME SMTPResponse which is triggered after the connection is established to the SMTP Server It will write the next SMTPRequest to the SMTPClientSession with the right SMTPResponseCallback added.
